Start the program.
Input the double variable type, 1st number, let's name it x.
If its not a number, go back and ask 1st number again. Display invaild entry type again.
Input the double variable type, 2nd number, let's call this y.
assign an answer variable as double variable named as z.
Perform addition x+y=z.
Display Addition=z.
Perform subtraction x-y=z.
Display subtraction=z.
Perform multiplication x*y=z.
Display multiplication=z.
Perform Division x/y=z.
Display Division=z.
End of the program.


